19c5739.jpg&h=1f28c4d1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n探訪家住市值600萬淘大花園香港精英中產一家<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/20/084422_7efa9478fe84b4938c96f4ecf52cc415.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F20%2F084422_7efa9478fe84b4938c96f4ecf52cc415.jpg&h=9a78570d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n老人：你看...香港班傻西幾百萬買間納米樓..哈哈...哈哈...<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/20/084606_43513e78aeb238c63fb2c3824dfd42e6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F20%2F084606_43513e78aeb238c63fb2c3824dfd42e6.jpg&h=3d1bd080&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/20/084607_a51ee980eb67416a235df1b3888bc02d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F20%2F084607_a51ee980eb67416a235df1b3888bc02d.jpg&h=6c754ae8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n正啊，豆腐細五臟俱全！🐷<br />\n<img src=\"http://livedoor.blogimg.jp/all_nations/imgs/e/0/e08e7c56.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Flivedoor.blogimg.jp%2Fall_nations%2Fimgs%2Fe%2F0%2Fe08e7c56.jpg&h=57a052f1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n福氣到極點😻😻😻<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">超落後、超唔環保深圳你睇下幾多白煙</span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/11/074118_dd7e45444da53dcb3924d3b86c070673.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F11%2F074118_dd7e45444da53dcb3924d3b86c070673.jpg&h=a9841ad1&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/11/074119_dd7e45444da53dcb3924d3b86c070673.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F11%2F074119_dd7e45444da53dcb3924d3b86c070673.jpg&h=41938a70&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/11/074119_7da590847f7dd2ad9cff8bb6a66fc5a1.j